{quote}each time I start Sourcetree, I have a popup asking me to install the LFS Adapter. This popup shows once foreach of my repo. And even if I check the "Don't ask me again", it keeps showing each time I restart Sourcetree. This is REALLY annoying and very error-prone.
{quote}
--STSP-6067

{quote}Our web proxy allows me to to access atlassian.com and I'm able to manually download (in my browser) the file that the installer cannot download ([https://downloads.atlassian.com/software/sourcetree/windows/PortableGcmSt-1.8.1.6.7z]). The installer doesn't seem to be using the proxy.
{quote}
